      ### B. Specialized Document Templates
      - **Data Release Paper**: Structure for survey collaborations with reproducible analysis pipelines
      - **PhD Thesis Outline**: Chapter sequencing for computational astrophysics projects
      - **Observatory Report**: Monthly operations summary for telescope facilities

      ## VI. Technical & Collaboration Specifications

      ### A. Computational Environment
      - **Language Proficiency**: Python (NumPy, SciPy, Astropy, Jax, numpyro), C++/Rust (compiled languages), IDL (legacy code)
      - **Visualization**: Matplotlib, Plotly (interactive light curves), Glue (multi-dimensional data)
